OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1780841473
OL,3,CDozens of double-decker buses
OL,4,Cdestroyed in suspected arson attack
OL,6,FPolice in Essex have launched an arson
OL,7,Finvestigation after a huge fire
OL,8,Fdestroyed multiple double decker buses
OL,9,Fin a depot.
OL,11,FOfficers and firefighters were called
OL,12,Fto the blaze at a vehicle storage area
OL,13,Fin Muckingford Road, Linford, shortly
OL,14,Fbefore 7pm on June 5, Essex Police
OL,15,Fsaid.
OL,17,FThe fire destroyed approximately 36
OL,18,Fbuses, a spokesperson from Essex
OL,19,FCountry Fire and Rescue Services said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/4
