OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1780841473
OL,3,CDozens of double-decker buses
OL,4,Cdestroyed in suspected arson attack
OL,6,FPolice are treating the incident as
OL,7,Fsuspected arson, but no arrests have
OL,8,Fbeen made so-far.
OL,10,FDrone footage from the scene showed
OL,11,Fhuge plumes of grey smoke spiraling
OL,12,Finto the air and multiple buses
OL,13,Freduced to scrap.
OL,15,FIt took more than two hours to put out
OL,16,Fthe fire, and several roads in the
OL,17,Farea had to be closed.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/4
