OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1780841473
OL,3,CDozens of double-decker buses
OL,4,Cdestroyed in suspected arson attack
OL,6,F"This was a significant and
OL,7,Fchallenging incident involving a large
OL,8,Fnumber of vehicles," said fire station
OL,9,Fmanager Lee Hurst.
OL,11,F"Thanks to the hard work and
OL,12,Fprofessionalism of our firefighters,
OL,13,Fsupported by Essex Police, utility
OL,14,Fproviders and local farmers, we were
OL,15,Fable to bring the fire under control
OL,16,Fand prevent further spread."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/4
